snippet.title: Chiki Chiki Machine Mou Race 2 - In Space (3DO) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
I don't think the 3DO has any worse racing games, so I'm callign It the worst of the system and I'd be Impressed and have to force myself to play It to torture myself If you know of anything worse on the system.

But what's the point of the cool bone car that you don't drive In the races, Is It because Dick stole something from It or because It morpths Into the other racers? I can't understand Japanese so... these are my two assumptions.
